GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 15th October, 2001
23 Asvina, 1923 (S)
The undersigned is directed to state that with effect from the 15th
October, 2001: -
i)
Shri Jaswant Singh relinquished the charge of the office of Minister
of Defence. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of
Minister of External Affairs.
Shri George Fernandes assumed the charge of the office of Minister
of Defence.
iii) Shri Harin Pathak assumed the charge of the office of Minister of
State in the Department of Defence Production and Supplies in the
Ministry of Defence.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
for Cabinet Secretary.
